/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6233cfcb6579fa46ee5b0b9c297b0931cd35419d","tid":206702,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T14:04:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>笑吓啦</blockquote><br />\n笑好攰，個人好假</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好明白樓主呢點，我自己對外都成日笑，只不過唔想俾人知自己係極度負面嘅人，只會對最fd嘅fd訴苦</blockquote><br />\n係別人面前係好開心，但其實好討厭自己咁做</blockquote><br />\n因為你覺得咁樣做唔係做緊你自己 ?<br />\n<br />\n咁如果你做返自己既時候<br />\n你會點樣呀"},{"pid":"be9a74e14d077e6b57d6025ec7f6b03bf7e2eebd","tid":206702,"uid":10243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T14:05:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打 我前排都係咁 覺得人生好冇意義<br />\n你會唔會考慮 試下搵知己暢談一番<br />\n可能可以重新搵到活下去既動力呢</blockquote><br />\n冇傾訴對象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係我疏離人</blockquote><br />\n點解會疏離咗既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為我同佢地太大分別，日日就係諗玩乜，打乜機，我就係要努力讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我講d野同佢地根本對牛彈琴，朋友，不了"},{"pid":"dfda15c4ffad324650f46f61364d51eee4a3853b","tid":206702,"uid":10243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T14:09:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>笑吓啦</blockquote><br />\n笑好攰，個人好假</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好明白樓主呢點，我自己對外都成日笑，只不過唔想俾人知自己係極度負面嘅人，只會對最fd嘅fd訴苦</blockquote><br />\n係別人面前係好開心，但其實好討厭自己咁做</blockquote><br />\n因為你覺得咁樣做唔係做緊你自己 ?<br />\n<br />\n咁如果你做返自己既時候<br />\n你會點樣呀</blockquote><br />\n因為我心入面根本唔認同佢地，根本整件事唔應該笑，但表露唔到，咪附和下，笑下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c75aef83bd5231cd771becf867f35ff17c2c3e","tid":206702,"uid":3700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T14:10:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打 我前排都係咁 覺得人生好冇意義<br />\n你會唔會考慮 試下搵知己暢談一番<br />\n可能可以重新搵到活下去既動力呢</blockquote><br />\n冇傾訴對象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係我疏離人</blockquote><br />\n點解會疏離咗既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為我同佢地太大分別，日日就係諗玩乜，打乜機，我就係要努力讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我講d野同佢地根本對牛彈琴，朋友，不了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打讀緊中學定大專？我本身中學又唔係多朋友，讀asso又同啲同學好難混熟，見面多數都係傾學校嘅野，所以平時都好少聯絡，所以成日都自己一個人"},{"pid":"0a7eab5ac89a9c08bfc8dd7db3b6846cc24b7802","tid":206702,"uid":10243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T14:13:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打 我前排都係咁 覺得人生好冇意義<br />\n你會唔會考慮 試下搵知己暢談一番<br />\n可能可以重新搵到活下去既動力呢</blockquote><br />\n冇傾訴對象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係我疏離人</blockquote><br />\n點解會疏離咗既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為我同佢地太大分別，日日就係諗玩乜，打乜機，我就係要努力讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我講d野同佢地根本對牛彈琴，朋友，不了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打讀緊中學定大專？我本身中學又唔係多朋友，讀asso又同啲同學好難混熟，見面多數都係傾學校嘅野，所以平時都好少聯絡，所以成日都自己一個人</blockquote><br />\n大專，一啲非主流degree program，情況同你差唔多"},{"pid":"5d3f9dac45c8fc803d5c411034d7a645c8eb3f2c","tid":206702,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T14:19:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打 我前排都係咁 覺得人生好冇意義<br />\n你會唔會考慮 試下搵知己暢談一番<br />\n可能可以重新搵到活下去既動力呢</blockquote><br />\n冇傾訴對象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係我疏離人</blockquote><br />\n點解會疏離咗既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為我同佢地太大分別，日日就係諗玩乜，打乜機，我就係要努力讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我講d野同佢地根本對牛彈琴，朋友，不了</blockquote><br />\n你係咪諗多左<br />\n朋友，同學，同事<br />\n三樣野係完全唔一樣既東西<br />\n請唔好搞錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同學係同學，純粹係因為你地係同一個地方學習，並唔係朋友<br />\n同事亦一樣<br />\n有共同話題共同興趣既，先叫朋友<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}